          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The following corrections were taken into account",
                " A. In flux determination for fiss. detector",
                "      Losses in pulses due to the discrimination",
                "    Threshold",
                "      Self-absorption in the layer",
                "      Laboratory angular distribution of fragments",
                "    all not exceed 2.5 +- 1.%",
                "    Effect of D(d,np)D neutrons on the fission counts",
                "    was 1.0+-.5% for En=8.5 MeV and 18.+-.4 for",
                "    En=10.5 MeV.",
                "    Corrections for (d,n) neutrons from the struct.",
                "    materials were determined by experiments and",
                "    were 1.0+-.5% for En=6.54 MeV and 11.+-1.%",
                "    for En=10.50 MeV.",
                "    The accuracy of flux determination by fission",
                "    chamber was evaluated from 1.to 4.% without",
                "    the uncertainty in the (n,f) cross-section",
                " B. In flux determination by activation method",
                "      Background effects of (d,n) neutrons",
                "      Decrease in the neutron flux density along the",
                "    sample thickness",
                "      Flux variation in time",
                "    The accuracy of flux determination by activation",
                "    method was not better than 1.% for En=6.54",
                "    MeV and 3.% for En=10.5 MeV without the uncertainty",
                "    in the (n,a) and (n,p) cross-sections."
              ]
            }
          ],
